com.cerner.beadledom.pagination.parameters

Class OffsetParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.beadledom.pagination.parameters.OffsetParameter

  • public class OffsetParameter
extends Object
    Represent the offset parameter used for pagination.

    The validation rules needed for a offset parameter are contained here so that the same rules may be applied consistently across all paged resources.

    Since:
    3.1
    Author:
    Brian van de Boogaard, Will Pruyn
